summary: Married November 9, 1951 to Jane Frances Smith (1953) and Kathleen M. Smith. 9 years later they had 3 children. The couple moved to Omaha, Nebraska, where they have lived ever since. They have three children and one grandchild. Their son was born in 1931 and died in 1966.
